headline: Outside Inc. Announces Festival Headliners for Third Annual ‘Outside Days’ Presented by Capital One and REI Co-op
summary: BOULDER, Colo., December 03, 2025--Outside Interactive Inc., in partnership with the State of Colorado's Outdoor Recreation Industry Office and presented by Capital One and REI Co-op, today announced that Outside Days, previously known as Outside Festival & Summit, will return to downtown Denver from May 28 – 31, 2026, and feature headliners Death Cab for Cutie, My Morning Jacket, Cage The Elephant, Tash Sultana, Goth Babe, Japanese Breakfast, The Flaming Lips, Dawes, and more.
